422, 'Though I’m tempted by the call of the sea, I resist. It can’t claim me.In a way I’m stronger than the waves and I feel good about that.', 1602, 0), (155423, 'We all eventually find that life is a series of adjustments, but anything can be overcome when there is love around you. Once can be strong on their own, but there is greater strength in knowing when to rely on others.', 29252, 0), (155424, 'I believe i am hard as a stone, but even a stone breaks if you smash it real hard.....', 15747, 0), (155425, 'If you do not feel ashamed of anything, then you can do whatever you like', 33, 0), (155426, 'The human spirit is to grow strong by conflict.', 3573, 0), (155427, 'It is difficult for a man laden with riches to climb the steep path, that leads to bliss', 33, 0), (155428, 'He was handsome and strong, but somehow that wasn''t enough for him. He also felt the need to be tough and inured to hardship... But how was he to come by that quality in this luminous garden, where all manner of fruit was to be had for the picking?', 3492, 0), (155429, 'Who are the learned? Those who practice what they know', 33, 0), (155430, 'My dark days made me strong. Or maybe I already was strong, and they made me prove it.', 14688, 0), (155431, 'It took strength to be quiet. It took strength to be kind. It took strength to let other people''s cruelty bounce right off of you.', 5947, 0), (155432, 'We are all crazy enough to hear the voices but not strong enough to listen', 2891, 0), (155433, 'Failure is a part of life. Success teaches you nothing, but failure teaches you resilience. It teaches you to pick yourself up and try again.', 12062, 0), (155434, 'You can''t go back and I think that''s the point of all to grow and grow until you don''t want to anymore.', 3305, 0), (155435, 'The world was so much more forgiving of strength when it took on the appearance of weakness.', 3748, 0), (155436, 'I knew what I stood for, even if nobody else did. I knew the piece of me on the inside, truer 